Loops: If we have to perform some repetitive task
       If we have group of something and we wish to perform some action over that group

-while loop
   variable
   while(applyConditionOverTheVariable)
   {
      This will execute only if condition is true
      I/D;
   }
-for loop

   for(variable; applyConditionOverTheVariable;I/D)
   {
      This will execute only if condition is true

   }
-advanced for loop

